  "remarks": "Bashir Mohamed Mahamoud is a military commander of Al-Shabaab. Mahamoud was also one of approximately ten members on Al-Shabaab's leadership council as of late 2008. Mahamoud and an associate were in charge of the 10 Jun 2009 mortar attack against the Somali Transitional Federal Government in Mogadishu.",
